"""Tests for epoch derivation correctness and the /epochs endpoint.

Slice D. Pins three behaviors:

1. Statusline-only sessions show their epoch (no hook activity yet).
2. epoch_id is consistent across paths — session detail's epochs[] and
   IdEnricher.epoch_id (for the same epoch) produce the same hash.
3. /api/v2/sessions/{session_id}/epochs returns the same list as the
   nested epochs[] in session detail.
4. ended_at on closed epochs reflects claude_log_pid_deaths.observed_at
   when a death exists for the (pid, source_system, cwd) tuple.
"""

